{"tid":1470221,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解一定要叫去機場示威先得","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:17.000Z","uid":10905,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5876925765334d9bdd4936a0c63562e43bf260d8","tid":1470221,"uid":10905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:32:51.000Z","msg":"既然出左禁制令唔比示威<br />\n咁點解我地一定要用示威呢樣野做我地既目的<br />\n好似一開頭咁接機送機又得<br />\n作為香港市民歡迎遊客又得<br />\n整左d字句送俾遊客唔得？<br />\n宣傳香港唔得？<br />\n派單張唔得？<br />\n<br />\n其實入機場有好多野做<br />\n去食野又得<br />\n去睇戲又得<br />\n我黎涼冷氣都得<br />\n點解偏偏係要用示威去形容自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只要冇組織冇人講過話去機場示威/集結<br />\n冇講過著咩衫戴d咩<br />\n咁機管局又好咩人都好又可以做到d咩<br />\n<br />\nOk就算有人搞事既咪唔好理佢囉<br />\n反正又冇人示威緊<br />\n不過如果見到佢做d危險野就梗係一要禁低佢啦<br />\n市民權利黎嫁嘛<br />\n<br />\n咁玩又可以多d人參與<br />\n係咪？"},{"pid":"e80d0020d0a44b6c65ba1ac1e7915f197bfd7802","tid":1470221,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:33:59.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"930977554bfe037dec0dbcfb0bc315dfecb8b21c","tid":1470221,"uid":249761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔快啲買飛今晚去機場睇戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/ticketing/overview?cid=0007&amp;sid=4816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uacinemas.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fticketing%2Foverview%3Fcid%3D0007%26sid%3D4816&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=00fc108a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/ticketing/overview?cid=0007&amp;sid=4816</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GK3rjkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGK3rjkq.jpg&h=967ed2e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b69c008c16e7efd81fe6f97ed8342c4775cbb4f","tid":1470221,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"仲有指定區域可以示威 就要去做 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"b45ade04cce56d729f8185f479c9e4c08ef8c425","tid":1470221,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"930977554bfe037dec0dbcfb0bc315dfecb8b21c","tid":1470221,"uid":249761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:34:20.000Z","msg":"連登仔快啲買飛今晚去機場睇戲<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/ticketing/overview?cid=0007&amp;sid=4816\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uacinemas.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fticketing%2Foverview%3Fcid%3D0007%26sid%3D4816&d=XnUAAdw%2Byae55KAVvns6wwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=00fc108a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uacinemas.com.hk/chi/ticketing/overview?cid=0007&amp;sid=4816</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GK3rjkq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGK3rjkq.jpg&h=967ed2e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"我慣左去到機場，行幾個鐘先walk in買飛"}]}